    "This yields an approximate expression for the amplitudes in order O(γ):b 2 (t) ∼ b 2 (0) 1 - γF 2π t 2 + ḃ2 (0) t - iω 2 t 2, (B6)where F is the spectral weight, given by:F = ∞ -∞ [f (ω q)] 2 dω q (B7) and ω = 1 F ∞ -∞dω q (ω q -ω 0)[f (ω q)] 2.",
